"      What is this drug used for?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10014083\">",
"      What do I need to tell my doctor before I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10014088\">",
"      What are some things I need to know or do while I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10014089\">",
"      What are some side effects of this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10014091\">",
"      What are some side effects that I need to call my doctor about right away?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10014086\">",
"      How is this drug best taken?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10014087\">",
"      What do I do if I miss a dose?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10014092\">",
"      How do I store and/or throw out this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10014093\">",
"      General drug facts",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"   </ul>",
"  </div>",
"  <h1>",
"   RELATED TOPICS",
"  </h1>",
"  <div id=\"relatedTopics\">",
"   <ul>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"drug drug_general\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?4/46/4836?source=related_link\">",
"      Gatifloxacin: Drug information",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"drug drug_pediatric\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?34/19/35123?source=related_link\">",
